description:
In data for compute.instance.exists notification, "audit_period_begining" key is misspelled. Should be "audit_period_beginning". 
We should fix this before essex releases & folks start to rely on this :-> 

Fix code  & wiki documentation.
title: Typo in system usage data: 'audit_period_begining'  should be 'audit_period_beginning'
